Package com.camerontec.catalys.server.adapter.mq

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    MQConstants Deprecated
    The generated attribute classes should be used instead.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MQConsumer
    Consumes messages from MQSeries and fires them to the Catalys engine.
    MQHelper
    This class is intended to wrap behaviour needed to connect to and use MQSeries queues.
    MQProducer
    This type of object is configured at the end of a chain of Message Processors passing messages from a Cameron Systems FIX engine to an MQ queue.
    MQSharedConsumer
    Consumes messages from MQSeries and fires them to Catalys.
    MQSharedConsumerFactory
    The purpose of this factory is to keep track of MQSharedConsumer instances.
    MQTransformer
    Standard ITransformer for converting between Catalys messages and our default MQSeries data format.
    OlympicRawTransformer
    Transformer derived from the StandardFixTransformer but altering the byte array parameter to remove the leading SOH and to add a trailing SOH in case there is a leading SOH and no trailing SOH.
